boxed environment can safely render untrusted templates.\n-   AsyncIO support for generating templates and calling async\n    functions.\n-   I18N support with Babel.\n-   Templates are compiled to optimized Python code just-in-time and\n    cached, or can be compiled ahead-of-time.\n-   Exceptions point to the correct line in templates to make debugging\n    easier.\n-   Extensible filters, tests, functions, and even syntax."}},{"id":"7df2851d-c7b7-46bf-9ab5-c14c281822e8","values":[-0.1022929772734642,0.1078801304101944,0.004259602166712284,0.010571924969553947,0.06194806098937988,-0.044240545481443405,-0.0030474590603262186,0.05102842301130295,-0.01719333790242672,0.014427857473492622,-0.008599254302680492,-0.039823275059461594,0.04703488200902939,-0.0029446077533066273,0.09557484835386276,0.08522164821624756,0.01925692707300186,0.013853013515472412,0.0008604638860560954,-0.04895913600921631,0.05890790373086929,0.049286387860774994,0.08591538667678833,0.06322339177131653,-0.05813644826412201,0.0036910909693688154,-0.0348101407289505,0.016249630600214005,0.039291609078645706,-0.020413357764482498,0.030000897124409676,0.07412181794643402,-0.041403163224458694,0.004641123581677675,0.041008323431015015,0.12375330179929733,0.04466240108013153,-0.030524808913469315,-0.053989555686712265,-0.04280078038573265,-0.03419230133295059,-0.0049873217940330505,-0.10058742761611938,-0.05349705368280411,-0.05463607981801033,-0.07263138890266418,0.012314017862081528,-0.059628117829561234,-0.008620912209153175,-0.0651070773601532,-0.08319533616304398,-0.048893287777900696,0.008365340530872345,-0.11052558571100235,0.036251652985811234,-0.03955400735139847,0.028110865503549576,-0.08655830472707748,-0.021237026900053024,-0.11295747756958008,0.013834495097398758,0.014808475971221924,0.016291096806526184,-0.009167401120066643,0.04954702407121658,-0.030317218974232674,-0.07095509022474289,0.09634462743997574,0.03750389814376831,0.008350258693099022,-0.03740616515278816,0.019631920382380486